    <section id="id1168348143514">
      <title>Answer the following questions:</title>
      <list id="id1168341598848" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Why was the girl unhappy?</item>
        <item>Did they become friends again? Why do you say so?</item>
      </list>
      <list id="id3336138" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Talk to a friend about your feelings when you are angry.</item>
        <item>Offer your friend sound advice when he/she is unhappy.</item>
        <item>Tick off all the characteristics that you recognize of yourself:</item>
      </list>
