      <list id="id6396260" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Draw a picture of yourself helping an elderly lady with her trolley in the supermarket.</item>
        <item>Everybody has now had an opportunity to talk to one another about all the good and bad things in people.</item>
        <item>We will now demonstrate to one another how we sometimes behave on the playground.</item>
      </list>
      <list id="id8267303" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Group activity: Dramatization.</item>
